<% content_for :title, "Help Center" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Prowl support center — get help with product page monitoring, alerts, scan results, and account management." %>

<div class="support-hero">
  <h1>How can we help?</h1>
  <p>Find answers, troubleshoot issues, or get in touch with our support team.</p>
</div>

<div class="support-content">
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Getting started</h3>
      <p>Learn how to set up Prowl, add product pages, and run your first scan.</p>
      <a href="/support/articles/getting-started" class="card-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Understanding scan results</h3>
      <p>Learn what each status means, how to read issue details, and what to do next.</p>
      <a href="/support/articles/understanding-scan-results" class="card-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Alerts and notifications</h3>
      <p>Configure when and how you get notified about product page issues.</p>
      <a href="/support/articles/alerts-and-notifications" class="card-link">Read guide &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Issue types</h3>
      <p>See every type of issue Prowl detects and what each one means for your store.</p>
      <a href="/support/articles/issue-types" class="card-link">View all issues &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Frequently asked questions</h3>
      <p>Quick answers to common questions about Prowl, billing, and scans.</p>
      <a href="/support/faq" class="card-link">Browse FAQ &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Contact support</h3>
      <p>Can't find what you need? Send us a message and we'll reply within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/support/contact" class="card-link">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="support-section">
    <div class="status-banner">
      <span class="status-dot"></span>
      <span class="status-text">All systems operational — scans running normally</span>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6d7175;">
      Prowl scans run daily at 6:00 AM UTC. If you need an immediate scan, use the "Scan now" button on any monitored product page inside the app.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
